# Metrics (`@triage-ops/metrics`)

Pure functions only — **no Prisma, no fetch, no env vars**.

## Functions

| Module | Export |
|--------|--------|
| `ghost.ts` | `countGhostIssues(issues, thresholdDays, now?)` |
| `zombie.ts` | `countZombieIssues(issues, thresholdDays, now?)` |
| `milestone-decay.ts` | `getMilestoneDecay(milestones, issues, now?)` |

## TDD required

- Add `*.test.ts` beside each module before or with implementation.
- Cover: empty input, boundary dates (exactly N days stale), zero matches, mixed states.
- Accept plain issue/milestone shapes — don't depend on Prisma types in this package.

## Usage

`apps/web/lib/services/metrics.ts` loads DB rows, maps to metric inputs, calls these functions.
